{
  "stem": "24364.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that's where the camp was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The camp was an old prison with 'His Majesty's Prison,' big letters on top.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it consisted of two blocks, block houses, which had separate cells.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I think, if I remember correctly, each house had about 400 single cells.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that's where the men went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the women went into a-- the women's camp, which consisted of, again, the corrugated iron sheet barracks, about 32 to one barrack.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the women's camp and the men's camp was divided by a huge wall.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there were walls around each of the camps separately and then a division wall in between with a gate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we came to Mauritius in December.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was unbearably hot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I never forget that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And on top of it, it was raining.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Mauritius, it rains all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "A friend of mine coined the expression, in Mauritius it rains with every [? where. ?] And it's true.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was really strange.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You could go and-- and here was sunshine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then you go over there maybe 20 feet and it rained.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was a lot of rain in Mauritius.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Mauritius is a-- a tropical island, which is about, I think it's-- it's in the southern hemisphere.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It's about, I think, 20 degrees south.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the weather actually is really not quite tropical, because it's surrounded by the sea.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But it's terribly humid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And that's one of the worst things about it, and hot, and mosquitoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It-- Mauritius was, I believe, discovered by the Portuguese sometime in the 1600s.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Then the Dutch took over and had it for maybe 100 years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And it's called actually after the Dutch stadholder, Prince Maurice of Nassau.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "That's what Mauritius was called after.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
